<paragraph blockId="23.[721,867,267,293]" box="[721,867,267,293]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[721,867,267,293]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">Subgroup 2</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="23.[189,1366,333,359]" box="[189,1366,333,359]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">Male tergites without silver spots, i.e., microtrichiose spots not reflecting, tergites 2+3 more convex.</paragraph>
